articles.author: Ben Collins
articles.title: NFL play-offs: Tampa Bay Buccaneers beat Philadelphia Eagles, Buffalo Bills also progress - BBC.com
articles.description: The Buffalo Bills beat the Pittsburgh Steelers while the Tampa Bay Buccaneers dump out the Philadelphia Eagles to clinch the final two spots in the divisional round.
articles.content: Philadelphia had more wins by the end of November than Tampa Bay managed all season as the Bucs came into the play-offs with a 9-8 record - the worst out of the 14 teams that progressed to the post-s… [+845 chars]
